ith its broad hands."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It is a pantomime expert that can create invisible but solid walls using miming gestures."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Emanations from its fingertips solidify the air into invisible walls that repel even harsh attacks."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"A skilled mime from birth, it gains the ability to create invisible objects as it matures."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its fingertips emit a peculiar force field that hardens air to create an actual wall."},{"version":"black","text":"It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air."},{"version":"white","text":"It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air."},{"version":"x","text":"Emanations from its fingertips solidify the air into invisible walls that repel even harsh attacks."},{"version":"y","text":"It is adept at conning people. It is said to be able to create walls out of thin air by miming."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions convince watchers that something unseeable actually exists. Once the watchers are convinced, the unseeable thing exists as if it were real."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions convince watchers that something unseeable actually exists. Once the watchers are convinced, the unseeable thing exists as if it were real."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Its pantomime skills are wonderful. You may become enraptured while watching it, but next thing you know, Mr. Mime has made a real wall."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It creates invisible walls with its pantomiming. If you don\u2019t act impressed, it will attack you with a double slap!"},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Always practicing its pantomime act. It makes enemies believe something exists that really doesn\u2019t."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Always practicing its pantomime act. It makes enemies believe something exists that really doesn\u2019t."},{"version":"sword","text":"The broadness of its hands may be no coincidence\u2014many scientists believe its palms became enlarged specifically for pantomiming."},{"version":"shield","text":"It\u2019s known for its top-notch pantomime skills. It protects itself from all sorts of attacks by emitting auras from its fingers to create walls."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"The behavior of this clown-like Pok\u00e9mon reminds one of pantomime. It creates invisible walls using a force emitted from its fingertips."}],"evo":{"name":"mime-jr","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"mr-mime","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":"mimic","known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"mr-rime","level":2,"min_level":42,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sp